ageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vox1665702666398.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vox1665702666398.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vox1665702666398.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vox1665702666398\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n trigger CornerButton_LClicked \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vox1665702666398__trigger_cornerbutton_lclicked_393762\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Interactive trigger that is activated when the user clicks the corner button of the Grid widget, with or without any combination of the <span class=\"ph keypress\">Shift</span>, <span class=\"ph keypress\">Alt</span>, and <span class=\"ph keypress\">Control</span> keys.\n </p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vox1665702666398_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vox1665702666398__codeblock_mm5_wxj_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger CornerButton_LClicked \n    params \n      numeric shiftKey : in \n    endparams \n\n    ; &lt;Your code here&gt; \n\n    end; trigger CornerButton_LClicked</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vox1665702666398__section_w738ab1b7b5_w739ab1b7_w740ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-colum